definitions.definition: An expression of mirth particular to the human species ; the sound heard in laughing; laughter .
examples: His deep laughs boomed through the room.

definitions.definition: Something that provokes mirth or scorn .
examples: Your new hat's an absolute laugh , dude.

main_definition: An expression of mirth particular to the human species ; the sound heard in laughing; laughter .
secondary_definitions: Something that provokes mirth or scorn .
( British , New Zealand ) A fun person.
